data.text:
I Got You Babe & The Bronx Duo - Set of two.

I GOT YOU BABE

Just like the classic song by Cher, our "I Got You Babe" lipstick has all the essence of deep love, rich soul and absolute togetherness. Let it be your go-to everyday choice that never lets you down and always has your back.

Ingredients:

CAPRYLIC/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE, OCTYLDODECANOL, POLYBUTENE, BIS-DIGLYCERYL POLYACYLADIPATE-2, POLYGLYCERYL-2 TRIISOSTEARATE, PENTAERYTHRITYL TETRABEHENATE, SYNTHETIC WAX, POLYETHYLENE, OZOKERITE, CAPRYLYL METHICONE, SILICA, HYDROGENATED MICROCRYSTALLINE WAX, JOJOBA (SIMMONDSIA CHINENSIS) SEED OIL, SODIUM MAGNESIUM SILVER PHOSPHATE, TOCOPHERYL ACETATE, PENTAERYTHRITYL TETRA-DI-t-BUTYL HYDROXYHYDROCINNAMATE, CI 77891, CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499, RED 7 LAKE (CI 15850)

THE BRONX

"The Bronx" is for the days and nights you just need some extra fun, edgy flavor for your next adventure. Can I get a side order of "attitude" to go with that?
